Package CommandManager

Interface ISlashCommand

All Known Implementing Classes:
AddChannel, Avatar, Define, EightBall, Menus, Ping, Purge, PurgeVCText, Restart, Shutdown, StarCheck, Stats, TopConcentrations, TopStars, UpdateCommands, WhoIs
public interface ISlashCommand
ISlashCommand is the command interface, all commands must use this interface to be recognized by the SlashCommandManager
